# Implementation Plan - Full Project Localization (next-intl)

Apply comprehensive localization to the Phdaot project using `next-intl` with path-based routing (`/[locale]/...`).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This plan involves moving all files currently in `src/app/` (except `[locale]` and `globals.css`) into the `src/app/[locale]/` directory. This is standard for `next-intl` but will temporarily break any hardcoded links that don't account for the locale prefix.

> [!TIP]
> We will implement a `navigation.ts` utility that provides localized `Link`, `useRouter`, and `usePathname` to make this transition seamless for developers.

